/* ==========================================
   VINCE TALK TOPICS — WORKING ON BREAK PHASE, LEVEL 1
   phase === "working.onBreak" && friendshipLevel === 1

   CHARACTER: Vince Rossi, Manager at Ruby's Diner
   → Patronizing, watching, counting money and time.
   → Acts like a friend while enforcing strict rules.
   → Hovers uncomfortably.

   WORKING ON BREAK L1 TONE:
   → Player is dishwasher on break.
   → Vince reminds them they are on his clock.
   → CRITICAL: Subtly manipulative, praising but pushing.

   CONTEXTS:
   dinerRubys_workingOnBreak_morning
   dinerRubys_workingOnBreak_afternoon
   dinerRubys_workingOnBreak_evening
========================================== */

