<<dialog "dinerManager">>James broke two glasses this morning. Two. That's ten dollars in pure shattered margins.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Accidents happen.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerManager">>Accidents are the excuse of the incompetent. I'm glad you don't drop plates.<</dialog>>
